  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为HealthTech的医疗数据平台画一张架构图，核心场景是患者记录系统通过多层安全架构访问存储。先从用户入口开始吧，主体叫HealthTech_PatientRecords。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，用户节点HealthTech_PatientRecords已创建。接下来是DNS层吗？我看到您提到了多层安全架构。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，第一层是DNS解析，用Route 53。不过这里有个细节——子图名字叫HealthTech_EMR_Sync，但里面的节点也叫HealthTech_EMR_Sync，这是故意设计的，表示EMR同步服务本身。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DNS",
        "R53",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，创建了DNS子图，包含R53节点，命名都统一为HealthTech_EMR_Sync。用户通过HTTPS连接到这一层对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DNS",
        "R53",
        "USER"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，USER到R53要标注HTTPS。接下来是CDN层，子图叫HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault，这里包含边缘节点、Lambda、证书管理和缓存四个组件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CDN",
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA",
        "CERT",
        "CACHE",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下命名：EDGE和LAMBDA都叫HealthTech_LabAnalyzer，CERT叫HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine，CACHE叫HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault。这样设计是为了体现功能复用吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA",
        "CERT",
        "CACHE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，LabAnalyzer服务同时承担边缘计算和Serverless处理，DiagnosticEngine专门做证书校验，HIPAA_Vault则是缓存层的安全合规标识。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA",
        "CERT",
        "CACHE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "CDN子图已创建。现在画存储层，子图也叫HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault？这和CDN子图名字相同，是否需要区分？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "STORAGE",
        "CDN"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这是有意为之，HIPAA_Vault贯穿多个层级表示统一的安全合规域。存储层包含OAI和FILES，OAI叫HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault，FILES叫HealthTech_PatientRecords。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "STORAGE",
        "OAI",
        "FILES"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "存储层已添加。现在连接各层：R53指向EDGE，然后EDGE→LAMBDA→CERT→CACHE，这样串行处理对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "R53",
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA",
        "CERT",
        "CACHE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "流程正确。但CACHE到OAI的连接要特殊标注——必须是OAI Only，这是安全策略，只有Origin Access Identity能访问存储。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CACHE",
        "OAI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加OAI Only标注。最后OAI连接到FILES完成数据访问链路。现在需要设置样式吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OAI",
        "FILES",
        "CACHE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，用颜色区分层级：USER用浅蓝#e3f2fd配深蓝边框，DNS用浅黄#fff8e1配深黄边框，CDN用浅粉#fce4ec配深红边框，STORAGE用浅绿#e8f5e9配深绿边框。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "DNS",
        "CDN",
        "STORAGE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "四种样式已应用。我检查一下整体结构——等等，发现一个问题：R53到EDGE的连接没有标注，但其他关键连接都有标注，HTTPS和OAI Only都很明确，这里是否需要补充？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "R53",
        "EDGE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "R53到EDGE是内部DNS解析后的标准转发，不需要特殊标注，保持简洁。但让我再看一下CDN内部的命名——EDGE和LAMBDA都显示为HealthTech_LabAnalyzer，视觉上会不会混淆？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA",
        "R53"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确实显示相同，但这是您要求的命名设计。如果担心可读性，可以在节点ID上区分，比如保留EDGE和LAMBDA作为技术标识，显示文本用HealthTech_LabAnalyzer。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "这样处理可以，技术ID保持唯一性，显示文本体现业务归属。再确认存储层：OAI和FILES的命名，一个是HIPAA_Vault，一个是PatientRecords，这体现了原始数据与访问代理的分离对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OAI",
        "FILES"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，OAI作为安全代理层，FILES是实际患者记录存储。整个架构从PatientRecords进入，经DNS、四层CDN处理，最终通过OAI安全访问存储，符合HIPAA合规路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "DNS",
        "CDN",
        "STORAGE",
        "OAI",
        "FILES"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还有一个细节——CERT节点叫HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine，这个命名需要调整吗？它实际做的是TLS证书验证，不是诊断引擎。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CERT",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
