      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "布局确认为Top-Bottom。所有元素已就位：USER→DNS(R53)→CDN(EDGE→LAMBDA→CERT→CACHE)→STORAGE(OAI→FILES)，样式和标注完整。",
