      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "再核对一下边的关系：R53到EDGE是无标注直连，CACHE到OAI有OAI Only，USER到R53有HTTPS，其他内部边都无标注。这个设计准确吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
